<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٩٢ سورة الليل]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة الليل <span class="c2">(٩٢)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٧]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَاللَّيْلِ إِذا يَغْشى <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَالنَّهارِ إِذا تَجَلَّى <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَما خَلَقَ الذَّكَرَ وَالْأُنْثى <span class="c2">(٣)</span> إِنَّ سَعْيَكُمْ لَشَتَّى <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطى وَاتَّقى <span class="c2">(٥)</span> وَصَدَّقَ بِالْحُسْنى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْيُسْرى <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١-<span class="c5"> وَاللَّيْلِ إِذا يَغْشى:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَاللَّيْلِ وأقسم بالليل.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>إِذا يَغْشى حين يعم ظلامه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> وَالنَّهارِ إِذا تَجَلَّى:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالنَّهارِ وبالنهار.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِذا تَجَلَّى إذا سطع ضوءه.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> وَما خَلَقَ الذَّكَرَ وَالْأُنْثى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَما خَلَقَ وبالذي خلق.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الذَّكَرَ وَالْأُنْثى من كل ما يتوالد.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> إِنَّ سَعْيَكُمْ لَشَتَّى:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لَشَتَّى لمختلف.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٥-<span class="c5"> فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطى وَاتَّقى:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطى أي أنفق فى سبيل الله.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَاتَّقى وخاف ربه.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٦-<span class="c5"> وَصَدَّقَ بِالْحُسْنى:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَصَدَّقَ وأيقن.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>بِالْحُسْنى بالفضيلة الحسنى، وهى الإيمان بالله عن علم.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٧-<span class="c5"> فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْيُسْرى:</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>